{"tid":2039105,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[會計L] 簽名師入！國安法下未來連工都無得返！","createTime":"2020-05-28T00:33:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-28T01:27:03.000Z","uid":70915,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"52e489144a7ebea7e4ef68d6cc7c787dd49882d4","tid":2039105,"uid":70915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T00:33:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">召喚簽名師</span><br />\n唔好同我講你手上無中資客呀！國安法搞到會計界係遲早嘅事，點可以唔發聲！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">工會搞左個聯署</span>，返工好罷工好，入黎簽個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />人數告急<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔使有牌會計師先簽得！524 527手足嘅努力，加上美國比曬彈藥，唔係寫個名都懶呀！<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n聯署傳送門：<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScvp3IIsUMfpKtxop7kMMsqkRIyl_VNKGx6stbKz3hlm-z6cw/viewform?usp=sf_link\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLScvp3IIsUMfpKtxop7kMMsqkRIyl_VNKGx6stbKz3hlm-z6cw%2Fviewform%3Fusp%3Dsf_link&d=%2FAUJPsyZ5YTgQdLV7Kr5Pl7Oh%2FyAFRgp1rU3tL1w%2BGY%3D&h=7919c00b\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScvp3IIsUMfpKtxop7kMMsqkRIyl_VNKGx6stbKz3hlm-z6cw/viewform?usp=sf_link</a><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">點解會計界響國安法下首當其衝？</span><br />\n<br />\n會計師、核數師每天都要接觸大量的商業、財務資料，其中一些牽涉商業機密、甚至政府機密、國家機密。<span style=\"color: red;\">當國安法伸延到香港實施，而且「國家政權」包括香港政府的話，涉及國家、國企、港府相關的任何會計紀錄、核數紀錄、甚至相關的政府文件，都有機會成為敏感資料</span>。因此，不單需要回到內地公幹的會計同業受到影響，留在香港工作的同業經電郵得到內地資料、或者純粹處理與國企、港府相關的交易文件，同樣有機會受到影響。"},{"pid":"10ba35d1727be1a1c3e1f42d1b0048a36f13c152","tid":2039105,"uid":70915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T00:33:38.000Z","msg":"自推十下 1/10"},{"pid":"e3aac3f7ccd6ba784ba01fa5f039e6012e6986a1","tid":2039105,"uid":70915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T00:34:26.000Z","msg":"推2/10 簽完share俾身邊做big4、會計嘅朋友！"},{"pid":"81123fa2fecbccd536fc96c812ad00e8d6ca222a","tid":2039105,"uid":70915,"like":0,"disl